It’s a sad day when some emotionally unstable folks leave voluntarily from your organization, and then subsequently sow discord within their new party in order to return some time later. One thing is certain, Belize is poorer today, than it was five years ago. Therefore, you failed.

Councilor Daniel Guerrero also featured with his final response to Ms Cal on the Cayo Highwway Hazard:

The G.O.B. did not  do anything on the James Adderly by pass. we would have prefer a huge 25-case of aluminun water pipes instead of a tiny patch of the pavement. The patch-job is as good as nothing. So this debate here is kind of useless. I thought it was pretty useless too when the Newspaper , the Sun published it. But I will engage it, because we must put an end to the subject. It’s getting kind of silly. Belizeans should pay attention to more serious things like in the referendum case, about the Logwood Treaty, and its economic implications. And you all in Cayo, you should prepare to teach the Sun and the Mail, like D.L.V guerrrrrrero how to do gutter journalism and that we do not and will not tolerate it.. Period!!!!
